---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
const title = 'Privacy Policy | whistleblowerawardcalc.com';
const description = 'Privacy policy for whistleblowerawardcalc.com — data collection, the case-review form, cookies, Google AdSense and Analytics, and your privacy rights.';
---
<BaseLayout title={title} description={description}>
  <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
  <p><strong>Effective date:</strong> January 1, 2026<br />
  <strong>Last updated:</strong> July 2026</p>
  <p>This privacy policy describes how whistleblowerawardcalc.com, operated by The Click Lab Agency LLC, collects, uses, and shares information when you use this website.</p>

  <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
  <p>Simply browsing the calculator and guides does not require you to provide personal information. We do not require registration, do not store calculator inputs on our servers, and do not collect your name, email address, or any other identifying information unless you contact us or submit the case-review form voluntarily. All calculator processing occurs in your browser &mdash; no data you enter into the calculator itself is transmitted to us.</p>
  <p>If you choose to submit the "Whistleblower" case-review form on the homepage, we collect your name, phone number, email address, the case details you provide, and a timestamp of your consent. This is separate from using the calculator and is entirely optional &mdash; see "The Case-Review Form and Attorney Sharing" below for what happens to this information.</p>
  <p>We use Google AdSense and Google Analytics, which may collect usage data as described below.</p>

  <h2>The Case-Review Form and Attorney Sharing</h2>
  <p>If you submit the case-review form, your name, phone number, email address, and case details are shared with one or more attorneys or their agents licensed to practice in your jurisdiction, so they can evaluate your situation and contact you about it. The Click Lab Agency LLC, which operates whistleblowerawardcalc.com, is not a law firm, does not provide legal advice, and does not vet, endorse, or guarantee the attorneys in this network. Submitting the form does not create an attorney-client relationship with The Click Lab Agency LLC or with any attorney until and unless that attorney separately agrees to represent you. The Click Lab Agency LLC may be compensated for these referrals.</p>
  <p>By submitting the form, you separately consent to be contacted by phone, text, and email &mdash; including by automated dialing technology &mdash; by The Click Lab Agency LLC and the attorneys or agents your information is shared with. That consent is not required to use any other part of this site, and you can decline it by not submitting the form.</p>

  <h2>Google Analytics</h2>
  <p>We use Google Analytics 4 (measurement ID G-XB1TWVB8JG) for aggregate, anonymized traffic data: pages viewed, session duration, geographic region, device type, and traffic source. This data cannot identify individual visitors. Opt out via the <a href="https://tools.google.com/dlpage/gaoptout" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Google Analytics opt-out browser add-on</a>.</p>

  <h2>Google AdSense and Cookies</h2>
  <p>We display advertising through Google AdSense (pub ID: ca-pub-6434377544325972). Google AdSense uses cookies to serve interest-based ads based on your prior site visits. Opt out at <a href="https://adssettings.google.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Google Ad Settings</a>. See <a href="https://policies.google.com/technologies/partner-sites" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Google's Privacy &amp; Terms</a> for how Google uses data on partner sites.</p>

  <h2>Opting Out</h2>
  <p>The simplest opt-out is not to submit the case-review form &mdash; every other part of the site (the calculator and guides) is fully usable without providing any personal information. If you already submitted the form and want your information removed or want to withdraw consent to be contacted, email <a href="mailto:hey@theclicklab.agency">hey@theclicklab.agency</a> with the subject line <code>[OPT-OUT]</code>, or visit <a href="https://theclicklab.agency/optout">theclicklab.agency/optout</a>.</p>

  <h2>California Privacy Rights (CCPA/CPRA)</h2>
  <p>California residents may request information about personal data collected, request deletion, and opt out of "sale" or "sharing" of personal information. Browsing the calculator and guides alone never involves collecting personal information, so there is nothing to sell or share from that activity. However, if you submit the case-review form, sharing your information with attorneys for compensation, as described above, may be considered a "sale" or "share" of personal information under the CCPA/CPRA, and you can opt out of it at any time using the channels in the "Opting Out" section above. Contact us at <a href="mailto:hey@theclicklab.agency">hey@theclicklab.agency</a> for other requests.</p>

  <h2>EU/UK Residents (GDPR)</h2>
  <p>The legal basis for processing the information you submit through the case-review form is your consent, which you may withdraw at any time using the channels in the "Opting Out" section above.</p>

  <h2>Children's Privacy</h2>
  <p>This site is not directed to children under 13. We do not knowingly collect information from children under 13.</p>

  <h2>Data Retention and Security</h2>
  <p>Calculator inputs are never transmitted to our servers. Case-review form submissions and email correspondence are transmitted securely and retained only as long as needed to fulfill the referral or respond to your message, plus a reasonable period afterward for record-keeping, unless you request deletion sooner.</p>

  <h2>Changes</h2>
  <p>We may update this policy periodically. The "Last updated" date above reflects the most recent revision.</p>

  <h2>Contact</h2>
  <p>Questions? Email <a href="mailto:hey@theclicklab.agency">hey@theclicklab.agency</a>.</p>
</BaseLayout>
